org.sbml.jsbml.math.parser

Class FormulaParserASTNode2

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbml.jsbml.math.parser.FormulaParserASTNode2
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FormulaParserASTNode2Constants, IFormulaParser

    public class FormulaParserASTNode2
extends Object
implements IFormulaParser, FormulaParserASTNode2Constants
    Class used to parse infix mathematical formula and returns a representation of it as an Abstract Syntax Tree (AST).

    Support almost the same syntax as defined in the LibSBML C-inspired infix notation taken from SBML Level 1 parser.

    Since:
    0.8
    Version:
    $Rev: 2377 $
    Author:
    Alexander Dörr, Nicolas Rodriguez, Victor Kofia
